      "full_name": "Joint Stock Company “ODK-Star”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “ODK-Star” is a developer and a serial producer of fuel-supply and control systems for air, ground and marine gas turbine engines. JSC “ODK-Star” is involved in the most important programmes of Russian engine building, including in the creation of D30-KP and PD-8 engines. D30-KP engines are installed on the military transport aircraft Il-76, used by the Russian Armed Forces in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. United Aircraft Corporation has started to develop the technical design in order to use PD-8 engines in military transport aircraft (IL-212). JSC “ODK-Star” therefore supports and benefits from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the illegal annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}